{"tid":1692192,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［集思廣益］召集各行各業嘅面孔一齊打造行動post","createTime":"2019-11-04T03:23:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-04T11:33:07.000Z","uid":245030,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"9d912cf3eb8c5a07b4f18467ab693e89617a8eee","tid":1692192,"uid":245030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T03:23:09.000Z","msg":"好多人成日都話勇武抗爭係唔會令依場<span style=\"color: gold;\">運動</span>獲得勝利，其實我認同&hellip;<br />\n因為依家根本只係<span style=\"color: gold;\">運動</span>而非<span style=\"color: red;\">革命，沒有革命是抗爭後要回家的。</span>而係武力唔對等，和理非亦未能再進化嘅時候；合法 有效率 符合不受傷不被捕主流意見嘅做法就係<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>大罷工</strong></span></span><br />\n其實都已經有好多post叫人罷工，但依個post嘅實際功用係<span style=\"color: orange;\">如何實行罷工</span>。其實罷工其中一個好重要嘅因素就係<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">成立工會</span></span>。<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">工會</span>原意是指基於共同利益而自發組織的社會團體，罷工係出於市民對政府不滿嘅發聲渠道，而工會嘅作用就係要保障罷工嘅員工會得到公平嘅對待。<br />\n而在以下情況，僱主不可即時解僱員工：<br />\n1. 懷孕及已向僱主發出懷孕通知<br />\n2. 放有薪病假期間<br />\n3. 向有關當局提供證據或資料時<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">4. 參加工會活動</span><br />\n5. 放工傷病假期間<br />\n<br />\n好多手足已經辭職全力投入<span style=\"color: gold;\">運動</span>，你叫佢地罷工都無意義，但連登集合左咁多冷氣軍師同和理非嘅同路人 請大家集思廣益，將依件事變為可能！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">基本法第三章 第二十七條 ：<br />\n香港居民享有言論、新聞、出版的自由，結社、集會、遊行、示威的自由，組織和參加工會、罷工的權利和自由。 </span></span>"},{"pid":"51908a9c7a3f48816bb2c23b4b8dcd4b658f4b05","tid":1692192,"uid":245030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T03:24:17.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"c4ddda904517e8de3b5cbfa20488a288dc017429","tid":1692192,"uid":245030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T03:24:47.000Z","msg":"甴近平"},{"pid":"000cadb674a08e72ba1cdad7355d72b5d2930107","tid":1692192,"uid":245030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T03:25:07.000Z","msg":"曱甴平"},{"pid":"7e4ee7b84aba2c0238b784f5f06e78f5f0eee23f","tid":1692192,"uid":245030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T03:25:19.000Z","msg":"習曱甴"},{"pid":"5c635dd3b4d0c36bd328943897c9d4b9284dc23d","tid":1692192,"uid":245030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T03:25:50.000Z","msg":"甴近平"},{"pid":"6e30f40a8550e464d42edf919fec6722e84e24b2","tid":1692192,"uid":245030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T03:26:02.000Z","msg":"曱甴平"},{"pid":"efb01ac2a7ae3cf0c17a6fb54c7417315c8f2bbe","tid":1692192,"uid":245030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T03:26:21.000Z","msg":"甴曱平"},{"pid":"92d67aeaa6d3744ff9cedaaae6a76f6613d36121","tid":1692192,"uid":245030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T03:26:32.000Z","msg":"習曱甴"},{"pid":"09920ae5e4de03017d46cc5f653fc48ea10f64ac","tid":1692192,"uid":107085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T03:33:59.000Z","msg":"幫推<br />\n同意要開始搞，呢個時候同期推罷工<br />\n就算罷工失敗最少都起碼成立咗工會"},{"pid":"b586813c655d617c36500d05216e20560a695124","tid":1692192,"uid":245030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T03:35:05.000Z","msg":"再推"},{"pid":"84d27229d3c405f56283a9c1f58d7770e8abb051","tid":1692192,"uid":245030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T03:35:21.000Z","msg":"一推再推"},{"pid":"98f2da6ce6404f1c237f5b78b1d4078ed79f0ff7","tid":1692192,"uid":245030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T03:42:18.000Z","msg":"推呀推 讓這post推"},{"pid":"4619578c728f65c50ce79167a700f4bddf1c8747","tid":1692192,"uid":302618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T03:54:06.000Z","msg":"打造 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02ab952703b60621a8c04c6cc5269b8765c494b6","tid":1692192,"uid